    "Thermal pictures have limited resolution compared to photos taken by other large cameras but contain the temperature of the nearby objects (Costa et al. 2013).",
    "According to Calderon et al. (2013) and Smigaj et al. (2015), thermal sensors are also used to monitor crops and detect agricultural diseases.",
